{"tid":1721462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（散水撚）不如十點前返屋企？","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:23:31.000Z","uid":130419,"like":176,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2b84de5d3c3799550f4d55deb204224d159f68","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"其實9-10點後基本上可以閃<br />\n一 商場/鋪頭閂晒 經濟攬炒達成<br />\n二 條街冇乜街坊路人掩護<br />\n三 狗隻輪更滿血捉手足<br />\n四 咁夜好易比便衣跟 鎖定目標<br />\n五 冇鐵冇巴士好難走<br />\n六 齊上齊落 hit and run be water<br />\n七 陣地傘陣呢幾個月證明冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八 手足太少 好易大圍捕 手足少一個就少一個 對家有無限資源同人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九 哨兵不足 <br />\n十 我唔想手足有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲人真心戀戰 <br />\n之前有巴打講得好岩 你咁夜搞 <br />\n成本高風險高回報低<br />\n呢幾個月總會有人落單加比人包抄 <br />\n由其夜晚成日開小花 記者同街坊都未必跟到<br />\n比人拉都冇人知 唔想又有浮屍同被跳樓<br />\n而且作用不大 條街都少車 狗車一衝過黎整咁大rb又阻自己逃跑路線 <br />\n最重要係冇軍裝唔代表冇便衣  到人地幾架車出黎果陣 人數不足你點都唔夠人打  點到即止目標達成就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有時都要識剛柔並重 要諗下策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩up下 覺得岩聽就聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：反對暴力同暴徒 還社會安寧"},{"pid":"b757c3f7113b3765d756bf187199d2809d1ebe28","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"推 一齊傾下"},{"pid":"af723f86fc0bc56560f0c9a6bc402eaffee68ce7","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"由其琴晚仲見到太子啲手足圍狗屋同打陣地 <br />\n睇到佢地來回跑又遮陣 見到都擔心都覺得佢地攰<br />\n人地係狗屋同警車休息夠就間中衝出黎又捉幾個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535f5171bc88243bb5f22ce99ff7b51f13852841","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73cd1f4302bdd7da9ecf3336e332832204313c17","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea8991c85370531a14d976da4ebc826c7781f37a","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"118f118ac396d146841867a7dcfe2541459dce1b","tid":1721462,"uid":253438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"推啊<br />\n要符合成本效益啊！"},{"pid":"b885eca43ce9846d6b81128b08cf978750e0d5e9","tid":1721462,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"朝早行動夜晚休息啦"},{"pid":"68bf1a9d78254fbcf75683036ef9f9c37b3503e9","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3922716fe8d05db6726109f0612b4ede5a69b100","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d646cfb5132eaa9283b845febaf09fa8b6a28f8","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8567e3fb5ecfa82f2b5f361f33b677a7c9ecfbdd","tid":1721462,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:15:19.000Z","msg":"可以參考 但唔fix 死因為可以隨時突擊狗屋"},{"pid":"25585e33d4edda0576d027a067e4291e3a9c4b21","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b749d404b3fa61143dd52f91949f3bbd3bf1474","tid":1721462,"uid":287064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"其實office hour完左就散得，搞咁耐消耗體力，回報又冇咁大，不如早啲訓回復好體力"},{"pid":"ae10510f34da6d46d7eece1cfdd326bbb60f9e68","tid":1721462,"uid":332051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1