"uid":130419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"見到岩岩<br />\n青衣 香港仔 元朗 葵芳 秀茂坪  屯門  粉嶺<br />\n捉左好多落單同大圍捕既手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:51:14.000Z","msg":"最唔想就係咁，唔實際。<br />\n夜晚危險，唔想送頭。<br />\n講極唔聽。"},{"pid":"cef4921524abdb6f1689a4b10f65323279ea4ba7","tid":1721462,"uid":150501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"3d11084ae1a50ba884458d43e3bf6bc856ac8157","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"851e26de9e4d85ffef6ab3a2925ea0a950fb0f13","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89ecf302d89f2048ec64842c6774b3958784600f","tid":1721462,"uid":295735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2b84de5d3c3799550f4d55deb204224d159f68","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"其實9-10點後基本上可以閃<br />\n一 商場/鋪頭閂晒 經濟攬炒達成<br />\n二 條街冇乜街坊路人掩護<br />\n三 狗隻輪更滿血捉手足<br />\n四 咁夜好易比便衣跟 鎖定目標<br />\n五 冇鐵冇巴士好難走<br />\n六 齊上齊落 hit and run be water<br />\n七 陣地傘陣呢幾個月證明冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八 手足太少 好易大圍捕 手足少一個就少一個 對家有無限資源同人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九 哨兵不足 <br />\n十 我唔想手足有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲人真心戀戰 <br />\n之前有巴打講得好岩 你咁夜搞 <br />\n成本高風險高回報低<br />\n呢幾個月總會有人落單加比人包抄 <br />\n由其夜晚成日開小花 記者同街坊都未必跟到<br />\n比人拉都冇人知 唔想又有浮屍同被跳樓<br />\n而且作用不大 條街都少車 狗車一衝過黎整咁大rb又阻自己逃跑路線 <br />\n最重要係冇軍裝唔代表冇便衣  到人地幾架車出黎果陣 人數不足你點都唔夠人打  點到即止目標達成就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有時都要識剛柔並重 要諗下策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鳩up下 覺得岩聽就聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：反對暴力同暴徒 還社會安寧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a677d9375a470bf9c30a572d0c82c673b752f348","tid":1721462,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"我都唔知拖黎做咩野<br />\n你人又小, 一定攻唔到狗, 連裝修都有難度<br />\n一係9企, 一係就狂走佬, 為咩?"},{"pid":"c7e4f05a1a8efac8224be73459739d2be0cb38c1","tid":1721462,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"企係度唔知做咩"},{"pid":"f605e8560c8462248da699538ddce0a80bb7dd2e","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a677d9375a470bf9c30a572d0c82c673b752f348","tid":1721462,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"我都唔知拖黎做咩野<br />\n你人又小, 一定攻唔到狗, 連裝修都有難度<br />\n一係9企, 一係就狂走佬, 為咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"有部分人覺得唔做啲野好似冇出過黎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dfe8e33acb111085069aab5526db1d1b627459","tid":1721462,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"081382ba211a1b34c0ce940437e60777c7495692","tid":1721462,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:28:05.000Z","msg":"葵涌邨 隔離就係狗舍 秒速有曱甴出車 晚晚都玩到勁夜 晚晚都多人被捕... 就為左堵下路 唔知為乜"},{"pid":"8cbc05e4361dc09a0f0b0edc37b0fcc186b21385","tid":1721462,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:28:58.000Z","msg":"Puah"},{"pid":"3b03bced7b90bc1404145e376048d9b588eefebb","tid":1721462,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc0df3774bd895da11b4326b974f34804a696e06","tid":1721462,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1